## Ingredients

- [ ] Sushi Rice
- [ ] Sushi ingredients (fish, avocado, etc.)

## Recipe

1. Spread the rice into a circle, then fill with the selected ingredients
1. Use plastic wrap to shape the ball into a triangular shape, then add a strip of Nori to hold the base
